  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd.\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc7 \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd : \u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd.\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b95\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0ba9\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel distribution in Jaffna district through fuel card: Jaffna district secretary Mahesan",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna District Secretary K. Maheson said that fuel will be provided only through fuel cards in Jaffna district.",
        "If he did not further inform in this regard, we have started the distribution of fuel cards before the introduction of the national work plan regarding fuel distribution system.",
        "Now a national job program has been introduced. We cannot ignore it. However, Jaffa. He said that the fuel card will continue to be issued in the district and the distribution system will continue to be carried out through it."
      ],
